-%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-qu%E1%BB%91c-th%C3%A1i-phu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-Gxx29uKwNNUsIeUh_RmD9Q">Phụng hạ Dương Thành quận vương thái phu nhân ân mệnh gia Đặng quốc thái phu nhân - 奉賀陽城郡王太夫人恩命加鄧國太夫人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A3o-h%C3%A0nh/poem-cIrCJ97JUtEsHI2-0_GJZw">Tảo hành - 早行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%E1%BB%AD-ly-1/poem-DMhzRqYfA9RgoCgkqGKZ7g">Thử ly 1 - 黍離 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%E1%BB%AD-ly-3/poem-9VOZ8XHMXuLvspmx-eclrg">Thử ly 3 - 黍離 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Ti%E1%BB%85n-V%C5%A9-V%C4%83n-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-nh%E1%BA%A5t-d%E1%BB%A5-Chi%C3%AAm-Th%C3%A0nh-qu%E1%BB%91c/poem-hpvGLVIfYIr3hr3G7hgjRA">Tiễn Vũ Văn Đồng nhất dụ Chiêm Thành quốc - 餞宇文同一諭占城國</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
